items.description: Tender, juicy, and perfectly spiced grilled chicken wrapped in pita bread or tortilla with delicious homemade yogurt-garlic sauce. Try this quick and easy grilled Chicken Shawarma and enjoy the explosion of Middle Eastern flavors with every bite!
